The paper discusses hyperparameters and their impact on generalization in Reinforcement Learning (RL). This topic falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on the interdependence of hyperparameters and their effects on RL generalization, which is a common problem in machine learning and AI research.
